# ⏱️ Pomodoro Timer App

A simple, modern, and responsive **Pomodoro Timer Application** built using **HTML, CSS, and Vanilla JavaScript**.

The application helps users stay productive by working in focused sessions and taking short breaks. It includes a **25-minute Focus Mode**, a **5-minute Short Break Mode**, Start, Pause, Reset functionality, dynamic status messages, and completed focus-session tracking.

This project was built as part of my **Frontend Development Journey — Day 23** to strengthen my understanding of JavaScript timers, application state, time formatting, DOM manipulation, event handling, and interval management.

---

## 🚀 Live Demo

🔗 **Live Website:**  https://timersetcheck.netlify.app/

---

## ✨ Features

- 🧠 25-minute Focus Mode
- ☕ 5-minute Short Break Mode
- ▶️ Start Timer
- ⏸️ Pause Timer
- 🔄 Reset Timer
- ▶️ Resume timer after pausing
- 🔀 Switch between Focus and Break modes
- ⏱️ Live countdown display
- 🎯 Automatic timer completion detection
- 🎉 Focus session completion message
- 🔢 Completed focus-session counter
- 💬 Dynamic timer status messages
- 🔒 Protection against multiple intervals
- 🎨 Active mode button styling
- 📱 Fully responsive design

