## 🔄 Complete Application Flow

```text
Application Opens
        │
        ▼
Focus Mode Selected
Timer = 25:00
        │
        ▼
User Clicks Start
        │
        ▼
startTimer()
        │
        ▼
Check if Timer Already Running
        │
        ├── Yes → Return
        │
        └── No
             │
             ▼
      setInterval() Starts
             │
             ▼
     Decrease timeLeft by 1
             │
             ▼
       Update Timer Display
             │
             ▼
       Has Timer Reached 0?
          │              │
         No             Yes
          │              │
          ▼              ▼
      Continue      completeTimer()
                         │
                         ▼
                 Stop the Interval
                         │
                         ▼
               Is Current Mode Focus?
                    │          │
                   Yes         No
                    │          │
                    ▼          ▼
              Increase      Show Break
              Sessions      Completion
                    │          Message
                    ▼
             Show Completion
                 Message
```

